      <p/>
      The original concept for this project was to view how the town of Blacksburg, VA changes from day to night.
      <p/>
      To achieve the mouseover effect, I used a combination of webkit's CSS3 support for <a href="http://www.webkit.org/blog/181/css-masks/">masks</a> and <a href="http://www.webkit.org/blog/1424/css3-gradients/">gradients</a>. As such, this demo will only work in Chrome and Safari.
