      This is an OpenGL-based animation engine I wrote for one of my college classes. I designed it to use the technique of capturing <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Key_frame">keyframes</a> of a robot and interpolating the position of the robot's limbs during playback. To help with the interpolation, I use <a href="http://www.cubic.org/docs/hermite.htm">Hermite Curves</a> to determine the position of points.
